dc_description_s: This data represents parks for Jefferson County, Wisconsin in 2019. [This coverage contains polygons for all known park and public lands in Jefferson; including municipal parks. Park Codes: H = Hunting; C = Co Parks; P = State Parks; O = Other; S = School Park; T = Town Park; L = Lake Management; F = Federal; Land MP = Municipal Parks (City or Village).]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
